"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">。</span></strong></span></p><p style="margin: 0px 8px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></span></strong></span></p><p><br/></p><section style="font-size: medium; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><section style="line-height: 25.6px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><section style="font-size: 1em; font-weight: inherit; font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px; text-decoration: inherit; margin-top: 2em; padding-top: 0.5em; padding-bottom: 0.5em; max-width: 100%; line-height: 25.6px; color: rgb(166, 166, 166); border-style: solid none none; border-top-width: 1px; border-top-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: -1.2em; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; border: medium; text-align: center; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="max-width: 100%; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 15px;"><strong style="max-width: 100%;"><span style="padding: 8px 23px; max-width: 100%; border-radius: 25px; font-weight: inherit; text-decoration: inherit; border-color: rgb(227, 108, 9); color: rgb(255, 255, 255); background-color: rgb(227, 108, 9);">他是中国古典音乐鉴赏家--刘雪枫</span></strong></span></p></section></section></section></section></section></section></section><p><br/></p><p style="margin-right: 8px; margin-left: 8px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-size: 15px;"></span><br/></p><p style="margin-right: 8px; margin-left: 8px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appuAhZGRFx3075/image/ueditor/84106600_1530088796.png" title=".png" alt="雪枫圆形。2.png"/></p><p style="margin: 0px 8px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="color: rgb(227, 108, 9);"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br/></span></strong></span></p><p style="margin: 0px 8px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="color: rgb(227, 108, 9);"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">他做主编</span></strong></span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">，使《爱乐》《留声机》中文版以及《交响世界》等杂志，凭着极高的专业度享誉乐坛。</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 8px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br/></p><p style="margin: 0px 8px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="color: rgb(227, 108, 9);"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">他著书立作</span></strong></span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">，接连出版《西方音乐史话》《日出时让悲伤终结》《音符上的奥地利》《德国音乐地图》等数十本老少皆宜的音乐读本。</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 8px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br/></p><p style="margin: 0px 8px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">此外，<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">他还写过《给孩子的音乐》，用深入浅出的方式，让孩子也能爱上古典音乐</span></strong>。</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 8px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br/></span></p><p style="margin: 0px 8px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appuAhZGRFx3075/image/ueditor/90731600_1530088796.jpg" title=".jpg" alt="6.piec.jpg"/></p><p style="margin: 0px 8px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(255, 169, 0); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br/></span></strong></span></p><p style="margin: 0px 8px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong><span style="color: rgb(227, 108, 9); font-family: 微软雅黑; letter-spacing: 1px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></span></strong><strong><span style="color: rgb(227, 108, 9); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">他也是音乐教育家、生活家</span></strong><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 28px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">，</span></strong>长期受邀在各大顶级学府和剧院举办音乐普及、艺术鉴赏讲座，成为千万人的音乐启蒙导师。</span><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></span></p><p style="margin-right: 8px; margin-left: 8px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></span></p><p style="margin: 0px 8px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: center; line-height: 1.75em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appuAhZGRFx3075/image/ueditor/96620500_1530088796.jpg" title=".jpg" alt="7.pic.jpg"/></p><p style="margin: 0px 8px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 13px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">▲2017年北京大学校友新年音乐会</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 8px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.75em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 13px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br/></span></p><p style="margin: 0px 8px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">雪枫谈古典音乐，总会有一种特别的魅力</span></strong><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">。</span></strong></p><p style="margin: 0px 8px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br/></p><p style="margin: 0px 8px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="color: rgb(227, 108, 9);"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">他Hold住世界名曲：</span></strong></span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">面向大众时，他不会丢出那些压得死人的复杂乐理，而会铺垫出许多细水长流的故事，他的经历，他的感受……<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">所以那些“名曲”也变得真挚，有强烈的共鸣</strong></span>。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br/></p><p style="margin: 0px 8px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="color: rgb(227, 108, 9);"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">他也喜欢谈音乐家：</span></strong></span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">贝多芬、李斯特、瓦格纳……但不是简单枯燥地注释，而是把这些作曲家请下神坛，化身成你自己、你的同学、你的朋友，感同身受去聆听。</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 8px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: center; line-height: 1.75em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br/></p><p style="margin: 0px 8px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">可惜古典音乐这么好，知道的人却太少了。</span></strong></p><p style="margin: 0px 8px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br/></p><p style="margin: 0px 8px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">很多人觉得古典音乐，是中产阶级或文艺青年的专利。自己不懂乐器和乐理，更听不懂古典音乐。</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 8px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br/></span></p><p style="margin: 0px 8px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">其实不是的。</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">雪枫坦言，<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">如果你觉得欣赏不了古典音乐，一定是你的方法错了</strong>。</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 8px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br/></span></p><p style="margin: 0px 8px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 28px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">他认为：</span><span style="color: rgb(227, 108, 9);"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 28px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">文学，才是普通人进入古典音乐大门的最佳途径</span></strong></span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 28px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">。</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 8px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; text-align: justify;"></span></p><p style="margin: 0px 8px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; text-align: justify;">只要你对文学故事感兴趣，就会对同样内容的古典音乐充满期待和好奇。</span><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br/></p><p style="margin: 0px 8px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appuAhZGRFx3075/image/ueditor/2170700_1530088797.cn/mmbiz_jpg/vgmxnh4aqqeiccjwqsajzjzyrzswa0o8elc1fomoctnjyhnoqicxzdlcvskv4h651opcdsqzlib74x2iamcgw8ftqa/640" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; height: auto !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; visibility: visible !important; width: auto !important;" width="638px"/></p><p style="margin: 0px 8px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">▲英国小提琴家Daniel Hope</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 8px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br/></p><p style="margin: 0px 8px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">所以，他希望可以讲述“<strong><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(227, 108, 9);">有故事的古典音乐</span></strong>”。</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 8px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br/></span></p><p style="margin: 0px 8px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">把文学故事和音乐连接起来，把那些作曲家请下神坛，化身成你自己、你的家人、你身边的小人物。</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 8px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.75em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br/></p><blockquote style="white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 10px; max-width: 100%; border-left: 3px solid rgb(219, 219, 219); color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 1px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 13px; line-height: 22.4px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">柏辽兹：</strong>雪枫说他是个<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">痴情少年，</strong>谱写出《罗密欧与朱丽叶交响曲》之前，就对最著名的朱丽叶的饰演者疯狂迷恋；</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 13px; line-height: 22.4px; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br/></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 1px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 13px; line-height: 22.4px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">李斯特：</strong>雪枫说李斯特跟浮士德一样，都有过失败的“<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">忘年恋</strong>”，在最彷徨痛苦的时候，谱写出震撼的《浮士德交响曲》；</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 13px; line-height: 22.4px; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br/></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 1px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 13px; line-height: 22.4px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">贝多芬：</strong>雪枫说作曲家都是<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">偏执狂</strong>，贝多芬写的《欢乐颂》太难演奏，宁可毁约也丝毫不改一个音符，才留下传世经典。</span></p></blockquote><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br/></p><p style="margin: 0px 8px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appuAhZGRFx3075/image/ueditor/8142300_1530088797.jpg" title=".jpg" alt="8.pic.jpg"/></p><p style="margin: 0px 8px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br/></p><p style="margin: 0px 8px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-wi